.TH ZLG 1
.SH NAME
zlg \- searchable compressed log archives
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B zlg
.I command
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B zlg
compresses plaintext logs into searchable .zlg archives and searches those archives without fully decompressing every chunk when summaries can skip irrelevant data.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B compress
Compress a plaintext log into a .zlg archive.
.TP
.B grep
Search a .zlg archive.
.TP
.B head
Print the first lines of a .zlg archive.
.TP
.B tail
Print the last lines of a .zlg archive.
.TP
.B stats
Show content and storage statistics.
.TP
.B info
Show archive layout information.
.TP
.B test
Verify archive integrity.
.TP
.B convert
Convert an already-compressed log into .zlg.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
zlg compress -m fast app.log app.log.zlg
zlg grep -r 'error|warn|fail' app.log.zlg
zlg grep --extract --top 'status=[a-z]+' app.log.zlg
zlg stats app.log.zlg
zlg tail -n 100 app.log.zlg
zlg convert app.log.gz app.log.zlg
.fi
